// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0227 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e51bb789-675f-5d69-b99b-eaeebc058371

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
